{"tid":583694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警涉「電子特賣城」偷29元耳機　被告留院缺席押後訊","createTime":"2018-03-07T08:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T05:33:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"820e6208d6568b6b0b437404a757fa70dbf5ff7e","tid":583694,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:15:58.000Z","msg":"休班警涉偷29元耳機　被告留院缺席押後訊 <br />\n<br />\n54歲休班男警涉嫌去年底在深水埗一間店舖盜竊一對價值29港元的白色耳機，店員發現後報警將該休班警拘捕。報稱警員的被告張志良被控一項盜竊罪，案件本來今(7日)在西九龍法院提堂，惟控方指被告現時正入住醫院而缺席聆訊，庭上未有透露入院原因，裁判官現將案押後至4月11日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告張志良於去年12月21日在深水埗福華街福仁商場的地舖「電子特賣城」內，偷竊一對白色耳機，價值29港元。"},{"pid":"ed95d8f0d94cc2329662c0406cee3b39d79df2df","tid":583694,"uid":21883,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/161925_5bdf788c5c87f0858b164a22bd161839.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F161925_5bdf788c5c87f0858b164a22bd161839.jpeg&h=4ad6f13b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c90d0f784ac26e998f8cb83ba1ee1dfbf1c13efb","tid":583694,"uid":46042,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"成日覺得呢間野好多人 偷咗都無人得閑理"},{"pid":"5ae304680e67e77d876f82830fd91d74cdf1f639","tid":583694,"uid":22422,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"我想知邊個教佢數學<br />\n糧 mpf 福利有邊樣低過$29？"},{"pid":"e1eabe3e43f536cd9ec4fbe22060ba3fc94f12b1","tid":583694,"uid":77717,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"5ae304680e67e77d876f82830fd91d74cdf1f639","tid":583694,"uid":22422,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:21:13.000Z","msg":"我想知邊個教佢數學<br />\n糧 mpf 福利有邊樣低過$29？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"有腦就唔會做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7469afa3